===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|badde}} "wicked, evil, morally depraved", originally "inferior, defective". Akin to {{etyl|ang}} {{term|bæddel||hermaphrodite|lang=ang}}, {{term|bædling||effeminate man|lang=ang}}

